extendedInfo.description: cab4me helps you to get a cab when you need it & see taxi ranks where available.* Brand-New UI* Better graphics for large screens* show distance of companies in result list* supports App2SD- Contacts access for quick pickup location search - Text messages allow you to send a cab phone number to friends easilyYou have questions? Feel free to contact us through Android Market any time.

reviews.title: Not worth downloading
reviews.comment: This app did not help me find a cab. Its user interface needs to be repolished and it a very slow.
reviews.author: Richard Davidson

reviews.comment: Not happy at all. I got 3 local  cab companies that I called and they didn\'t pick up. I had to go on line and call a different one. Too much drama.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Essential app!
reviews.comment: Accurate results of local taxi companies and with the option to add ones that are not on the database!  Any android owner should have this. A lifesaver for people in a tough spot trying to get home...  Being that this is all operated by one coder is nothing short of awesome! If you don\'t have this, get it!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Would like to see a premium option, no ads.

reviews.title: nope.
reviews.comment: Doesn\'t have any of my local taxi companies. Used the in-app option to add companies, waited 4 weeks. Local cabs still not listed, cabs from a city 30 miles away come up as my get a cab options. Sure, seems legit.   One last try, used it in Seattle while traveling. Cab never came.
reviews.author: Tim Boone

reviews.comment: Brilliant program no problems on my HTC HD
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Two years later........
reviews.comment: We have been submitting our taxi company information for over two years and they have still not added us. The sad part is that they have companies that are NOT taxi companies listed and also companies that are no longer in business, this is just another example of a taxi app that was created and had no support at all. Total fail!!!!
reviews.author: Glenn Edens

reviews.title: Garbage
reviews.comment: Only lists the companies that pay to be listed. Useless app really ...
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: USELESS if you want to actually get a cab
reviews.comment: Have attempted to use this app a few times now each time hoping that it might work for me, but all it seems good for is looking at a map with symbols supposedly meant to be nearby cabs that move around the little person that is meant to be you calling for a cab...... Yet to have any respond despite the countless number of them in the area, actually went and stood on side of main road nearby and watched cabs approach on my screen and see them drive by empty in real life.....
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: I\'ve submitted the same companies multiple times and they are never added. why even use the app at this point? I\'m ready to uninstall

reviews.comment: Works great around where I live n go out! South west uk
